Wayi, d gma.
Wa, d gma.
Tayi, d wletma.
ta, d wletma.
Ass-ayi d ass n rrbeḥ.
Ayyur, yettak-d tafat.
itran, ttɛassan-d fell-aneɣ.
Win i tuɣ yemma, nekk d arbib-is.
Ad ig Rebbi anda teddiḍ d tafat.
Ad ig Rebbi d sseɛd-is axir-is.
Ad ig Rebbi tewwi-d sseɛd deg ufus-is.
Sserseɣ-as sseɛd-is deg yirebbi-s.
Am win i yettrebbin ibki, la taḍut wala ayefki.
Medden ttrebbin tifunasin, kečč tettrebbiḍ acekkuḥ !
Awer tt-ig Rebbi d tindemmit.
Alukan ulac lukan !
Mi dliɣ fell-as, ufiɣ ḥaca Rebbi d umkan.
Keččini ruḥ, nekki ur stafeɣ ara.
Wiss ma yejji seg lehlak-ik.
Wiss ma yeḥla seg lehlak-is.
Tejjiḍ neɣ mazal ?
Teḥliḍ neɣ mazal ?
Ad ak-d-ifk Rebbi lǧebran.
Tuget n yimdanen, ttɛicen i wiyiḍ.
Ad ak-ifk Rebbi mejjuṭ, iqell-ak accaren.
Ad ak-ifk Rebbi ajeǧǧiḍ, iqell-ak accaren.
Lxedma-ayi teskanti-yi.
Xdem iḍ d wass, ayen i d-iqqimen steɛfu-t.
